{"tid":2293109,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"與李波函件如出一轍","createTime":"2020-11-20T04:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T10:22:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9c6824fb42f37692cf0f8ac2a52bf11d3e7b67","tid":2293109,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/V6Q3KJSIKRAWNMVYYGSCNTLD6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FV6Q3KJSIKRAWNMVYYGSCNTLD6E%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BaS5T01Y9%2BWuDWMC0%2BQyx7Y%3D&h=abf971a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FV6Q3KJSIKRAWNMVYYGSCNTLD6E%2F&h=347b5ded\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/V6Q3KJSIKRAWNMVYYGSCNTLD6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n與李波函件如出一轍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gaF7N3Y4Bt5xkV6BPemDyOAK3a0=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FLTLTLU36RDOPJKQ4O7SZPKDCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgaF7N3Y4Bt5xkV6BPemDyOAK3a0%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFLTLTLU36RDOPJKQ4O7SZPKDCM.jpg&h=b62c2f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李波<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中國政府秘密關押政治人物、維權律師的手段往往似曾相識，該人被捕後一般了無音訊，劇本發展下去，離不開親筆平安信、電視認罪等。今次家屬收到12人之中部份人的親筆平安信，與數年前被擄走的李波所寫的平安信，可說是如出一轍。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：12港人扣內地 家屬收報平安樣板信  強調吃得好沒被打「普通話進步了」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n桂民海仍在內地服刑<br />\n<br />\n經營銅鑼灣書店的李波在2015年12月從香港失蹤，其妻三度收到李波報平安電話，但明顯有人在旁監控。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，另一被失蹤的創辦人林榮基公開自己被強制扣押、輪流審問及逼迫認罪的經歷，他和書店經理胡志偉均指李波曾親口承認自己被跨境擄走。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"cd7e01d1420cb174e1fe1455c4f332e9b2c90ac3","tid":2293109,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}